      %h2
        General Counsel and Vice President of User Privacy
        %a{:name => 'general-counsel'} &nbsp;
      San Francisco

      = tapjoy_overview

      %p The General Counsel and Vice President of User Privacy will be responsible for defining and reviewing contracts, protecting our intellectual property rights, managing all legal and litigation issues, and providing hands-on legal counsel for all areas of the business. Reporting to the CEO, the General Counsel will also be responsible for defining and managing our user privacy policy, such that we demonstrate true thought and practice leadership in this emerging industry.

      %p We offer an opportunity to help build the largest mobile publishing company in the world. By providing sound legal expertise and in creating hundreds of app &quot;entrepreneurs&quot; with licensing and content deals around the world, the General Counsel will be a material contributor to Tapjoy's financial and industry success.

      %p
        %strong Role and Responsibilities
      %ul
        %li Defining and managing all client and business contract templates and assisting as necessary in deal negotiation and closing.
        %li Protecting our interests with respect to intellectual property and core company assets, including managing any and all litigation and legal processes with outside counsel.
        %li Defining, managing and articulating our global user privacy policies.

      %p
        %strong Professional Experience and Personal Qualities
      %ul
        %li Approximately 7-10 years of overall experience providing corporate legal counsel to the technology industry, preferably in the social media ecosystem (app development, online advertising, gaming, etc.)
        %li At least 3-5 years of experience negotiating complex business development deals
        %li An understanding of online user privacy issues, and the ability to build and manage a comprehensive policy that will set the standard for the industry
        %li Exceptional negotiating skills required
        %li Litigation experience preferred
        %li Undergraduate degree in a relevant discipline, MBA a plus, JD with an emphasis in corporate law required
        %li Self-motivator; gets high quality work done without a lot of noise
        %li High capacity, able to operate effectively in turbulent environment

      = about_tapjoy

